squad.Brief.takeaways | hasValue | Four candidate shapes for the post-install demo activity, written so Rob can pick fast. Each names: what the judge sees, which squaddies it asks of, what it requires that we don't yet have, what it risks. Not a recommendation — a menu. Decision is Rob's per law #5.
